OL,3,C'British FBI' to take over counter-
OL,4,Cterror and fraud investigations
OL,6,FA new national police force dubbed the
OL,7,F"British FBI" is to be set up under
OL,8,Fmajor reforms, the Home Secretary
OL,9,FShabana Mahmood has said.
OL,11,FThe National Police Service (NPS) will
OL,12,Ftake over responsibility for counter-
OL,13,Fterror, fraud and criminal gang
OL,14,Finvestigations.
OL,16,FIt will bring the work of existing
OL,17,Fagencies such as the National Crime
OL,18,FAgency (NCA) and regional organised
OL,19,Fcrime units under the same
OL,20,Forganisation.
