OL,3,C'British FBI' to take over counter-
OL,4,Cterror and fraud investigations
OL,6,FCounter Terror Policing (CTP) led by
OL,7,Fthe Metropolitan Police, the National
OL,8,FPolice Air Service run by West
OL,9,FYorkshire Police and the National
OL,10,FRoads Policing will all be merged into
OL,11,Fthe new NPS.
OL,13,FIt is hoped to lift the burden on
OL,14,Flocal police forces, who are believed
OL,15,Fto be diverting time and resources
OL,16,Faway from everyday policing against
OL,17,Fshoplifting and antisocial behaviour
OL,18,Fto deal with national policing issues.
