OL,3,C'British FBI' to take over counter-
OL,4,Cterror and fraud investigations
OL,6,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,7,Fannounced the move as she is set to
OL,8,Freveal reforms for policing in a White
OL,9,FPaper on Monday.
OL,11,F"The current policing model was built
OL,12,Ffor a different century," she said.
OL,14,F"Some local forces lack the skills or
OL,15,Fresources they need to fight complex
OL,16,Fmodern crime such as fraud, online
OL,17,Fchild abuse or organised criminal
OL,18,Fgangs.
