OL,3,C'British FBI' to take over counter-
OL,4,Cterror and fraud investigations
OL,6,F"We will create a new National Police
OL,7,FService ` dubbed "the British FBI" `
OL,8,Fdeploying world-class talent and state-
OL,9,Fof-the-art technology to track down
OL,10,Fand catch dangerous criminals.
OL,12,F"In doing so, local forces will be
OL,13,Fable to spend more time fighting crime
OL,14,Fin their communities."
OL,16,FThe NPS will be headed up by a
OL,17,FNational Police Commissioner who will
OL,18,Fbecome the most senior police chief in
OL,19,Fthe country.
