OL,3,C'British FBI' to take over counter-
OL,4,Cterror and fraud investigations
OL,6,FOnce up and running, it will set
OL,7,Fstandards and training for policing `
OL,8,Fand buy new technology such as facial
OL,9,Frecognition on behalf of all police
OL,10,Fforces.
OL,12,FThe service would share technology,
OL,13,Fintelligence and resources across
OL,14,Fborders and be created in stages
OL,15,Fworking alongside the NCA, CTP and
OL,16,Fregional organised crime units for the
OL,17,Ftransition.
OL,19,FIt will cover England and Wales but
OL,20,Fwill be able to operate in the wider
OL,21,FUK, a Home Office spokesperson said.
