OL,3,C'British FBI' to take over counter-
OL,4,Cterror and fraud investigations
OL,6,FA joint statement from the Met, CTP
OL,7,Fand the National Police Chiefs'
OL,8,FCouncil (NPCC) said: "Modern crime
OL,9,Frequires a modern policing response.
OL,10,FWe support and have been calling for
OL,11,Fthis ambitious step to bring together
OL,12,Fsome of the most capable policing
OL,13,Fteams in the country into a single
OL,14,FNational Police Service."
OL,16,FMs Mahmood is already expected to
OL,17,Fslash the overall number of forces
OL,18,Ffrom their current level of 43 under
OL,19,Fthe White Paper.
