OL,6,FThe Home Secretary has previously said
OL,7,Fthat the structure of 43 forces in
OL,8,FEngland and Wales is "irrational", and
OL,9,Fpolice chiefs such as Met Commissioner
OL,10,FSir Mark Rowley have already called
OL,11,Ffor radical reform of the set-up,
OL,12,Fbacking a system with fewer, but
OL,13,Flarger, forces.
